summary: These are my Orc preset, Face and Body.
descriptionHtml:
[center][color=#c27ba0][size=4][u][b][color=#d8d8d8]Hi !
If you don't really like to create your character, I hope this will help you.[/color]
[/b][/u][/size][/color][color=#f4f4f4]
This is a simple preset for a female Orc.[/color]

[img]data:image/png;base64,[/img]

[color=#d8d8d8][u][b][size=4]I don't guarantee that the face preset can work without:[/size][/b][/u][/color]
[list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666]CBBE [/url][/size]
[/list][list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/85649]RWoS[/url][/size][size=3] [/size][i][size=1](you need CBBE to run RWoS which replaces Orc's eyes.)
[/size][/i]
[/list][list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311]KS Hairdos[/url][/size][size=3] [size=1][i](you'll be able to run the FACE preset, [u]but not the hair[/u].) [/i][/size]
[/size]
[/list]
[size=3]And of course, if you want to use the body preset, you'll need [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666]CBBE[/url] and [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49015]BodySlide[/url], and if you want all the options, [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68000?tab=files]XP32 - XPMSE[/url] shall be installed.
[font=Trebuchet MS][size=2][u][i]
It's the first time I publish something, sorry if something isn't working.[/i][/u][/size][/font][/size]
[u][b]I just took a Vanilla preset to do this one, so, if any character in the game, changed by a mod or anything, looks like that, it's not my fault.
[/b][/u][/center]
author: Raszga
